      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "field_row",
        "fields": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "SPF/PC uses"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "Ctrl-Del+as the EOF (erase to end of field) key."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "The EOF key can be used whenever the cursor is in an unprotected"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "field.  It erases from the cursor location to the end of the field,"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "replacing all characters with blanks."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Using keyboard remapping (Panel 0.K), you may reassign the"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "EOF function other PFKeys or Ctrl/Alt key combinations."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
